Nokuli novayapostoli vaye kava li ve shi itavela pehovelo eshi va uda kutya okwa nyumuka .
( Lukas 24 : 11 ) Ovahongwa vaye ova ka dja ashike momalimbililo lwanima eshi vahapu vomuvo ve ke mu mona pomhito imwe vali .
Natango konima eshi Jesus a nyumunwa , okwa ka monika vali kovanhu ve dulife 500 . — 1 Ovakorinto 15 : 6 .
Eshi Jesus a kwatwa po nokudipawa , ovahongwa vaye ova li tava udifile ovanhu aveshe nouladi kombinga yenyumuko laye ; va udifila yo naavo ve mu dipaa .
( Oilonga 4 : 1 - 3 , 10 , 19 , 20 ; 5 : 27 - 32 ) Mbela ngeno ovahongwa vahapu ova dula ngoo okuudifa nouladi kutya Jesus okwa nyumuka ngeenge kava li lela ve na oushili ?
Oushili oyoo kutya enyumuko laJesus oko kwa kanghamena eitavelo lOvakriste okudja nale fiyo okunena .
Ehokololo olo li li momavangeli , li na sha nefyo nosho yo enyumuko laJesus , ola yandja oumbangi wa kola oo tau tu kumwe naasho sha popiwa kovanandjokonona .
Ngeenge owa lesha omavangeli oo noukeka , oto ka kala wa tomhwa kutya Jesus okwa dipawa nokwa nyumuka shili .
Otashi ka pameka yo eitavelo loye ngeenge owa kala u udite ko kutya omolwashike osho sha ningilwa .
Umwe womuvo , oTacitus , a dalwa mo 55 O.P . lwaapo , oo a shanga a ti : “ Kristus , oko kwa dja oshitya [ Ovakriste ] , okwa hepekwa neenghono kuPontius Pilatus pefimbo lomupangeli Tiberius . ”
Natango vamwe ovo va popya kombinga yaJesus ongaashi Suetonius ( mefelemudo lotete ) ; Omujuda , Josephus ( mefelemudo lotete ) ; nosho yo ngoloneya waBitinia , Plinius Munini ( pehovelo lefelemudo etivali ) .
( 1 Petrus 1 : 24 , 25 ) Shimwe vali , osha fa shi li ngaha kutya ovapataneki vaJesus kava li va shanga sha kombinga yaye , molwaashi inava hala ovanhu ve mu itavele nokukala ve mu lineekela .
Petrus , umwe womovayapostoli vaJesus , okwa shanga shi na sha nenyumuko laye a ti : “ Oye tuu ou Kalunga okwe mu nyumuna mefiku etitatu ndele e mu efa e liholole , Ye mwene , hakoshiwana ashishe , ndelenee kufye ava eendombwedi daye ngaashi Kalunga e tu hoolola nale , ofye ava twa lile ndele twa nwine pamwe naye , eshi a nyumuka movafi . ”
Evangeli laMateus ola popya kutya eshi ovatondi velongelokalunga va uda kutya Jesus okwa nyumunwa , ova li va tokola opo onghundana oyo iha tandavele . — Mateus 28 : 11 - 15 .
Mbela osho osha hala okutya Jesus ka li a hala ovanhu va ude kutya okwa nyumuka ?
Hasho nandenande . Petrus okwa shanga a ti : “ Ye okwe tu lombwela , tu udifile ovanhu noku va hepaululila Oye tuu ou Kalunga e mu ninga omutokoli wovanamwenyo nowovafi . ”
Ovakriste vashili osho hava ningi fiyo okunena . — Oilonga 10 : 42 .
“ Ngaashi oulunde wa etwa mounyuni komunhu umwe [ Adam ] , nefyo okoulunde . ” — Ovaroma 5 : 12
Mbela ngeno oto ka nyamukula ngahelipi ngeenge wa pulwa kutya : “ Owa hala okukala nomwenyo fiyo alushe ? ”
Ovanhu vahapu otashi dulika va nyamukule kutya heeno , ashike ove udite kutya oshinima sha tya ngaho itashi shiiva .
Otashi dulika va tye kutya efyo oli li oshitukulwa shonghalamwenyo , sha hala okutya otwa shitwa tu kale hatu fi .
Natu tye nee ngeno epulo ola lundululwa ndele tali kala ngaha : “ Owe lilongekidila okufya ? ”
Kashi na nee mbudi kutya omunhu oo a pulwa oku li monghalo ya tya ngahelipi , vahapu otava ka nyamukula kutya ahowe .
Ombiibeli otai ulike kutya Kalunga okwa shita ovanhu nehalo lokukala nomwenyo .
Oya ti : ‘ Okwa tula momutima wavo oukwaalushe . ’ — Omuudifi 3 : 11 .
Oshoshili kutya ovanhu ihava kala nomwenyo fiyo alushe .
Mbela Kalunga okwa ninga po sha opo a xwepopaleke onghalo oyo ?
Ombiibeli oya yandja omanyamukulo taa kumu omutima notaa yandje omatomheno a fimanenena kutya omolwashike Jesus a hepekwa nokudipawa .
Omatukulwa Ombiibeli atatu opehovelo embo laGenesis otae tu lombwele kutya Kalunga okwa popya kutya ovalihomboli votete , Adam naEva , otava dulu okukala nomwenyo waalushe nokwa li e va lombwela kutya oshike ve na okuninga opo vaha fye .
Ehokololo ola popya kutya ova dopa okudulika kuKalunga , nokungaho ova kanifa omwenyo waalushe .
Osho va ninga osha popiwa paunafangwa , novanhu vamwe nokuli ohave shi tale ko onga omahokololo onghuluyonale .
Ndele ngaashi ashike Omavangeli a popya oshili kombinga yaJesus , embo laGenesis nalo ola popya oshili .
Okunyona kwaAdam okwa ka etifa oidjemo ilipi ?
Ombiibeli oya ti : “ Ngaashi oulunde wa etwa mounyuni komunhu umwe [ Adam ] , nefyo okoulunde , osho nee efyo ole uya movanhu aveshe , shaashi aveshe va nyona . ”
Kungaho okwe lietela efyo nokwa kanifa omwenyo waalushe .
Oludalo laye alishe ola fyuulula oulunde kuye , nomolwaashi hatu vele , hatu kulupa nohatu fi .
Ndele mbela Kalunga oku na osho a ninga po opo a xwepopaleke onghalo oyo ?
Kalunga okwa ninga po elongekido opo a mangulule ovanhu ile a futile po osho sha kanifwa kuAdam , sha hala okutya omwenyo waalushe .
Ombiibeli oya popya mOvaroma 6 : 23 , ya ti : “ Ondjabi youlunde oyo efyo . ”
Osho otashi ulike kutya efyo oilanduliko youlunde .
Sha faafana , nafye ohatu hangwa kefyo olo li li oilanduliko youlunde molwaashi otwa nyona .
Nonande hafye twa nyona , otwa dalwa tu li ovalunde .
Onghee hano , Jehova okwa yandja Omona waye , Jesus , opo e tu kulile ‘ mondjabi youlunde . ’
Efyo laJesus ole tu yeululila omhito yoku ka kala nomwenyo waalushe
Molwaashi omunhu umwe a wanenena , Adam , okwe tu etela oulunde omolwokuhadulika , natango omunhu umwe a wanenena okwa li e na okudulika fiyo omefyo opo e tu mangulule moulunde .
Ombiibeli oye shi popya ngaha : “ Ngaashi kokuhadulika kwomunhu ou umwe ava vahapu va ninga ovalunde , osho yo kokudulika kwaau umwe ava vahapu tava ningi ovayuki . ”
Okwa li a dja mo meulu , ndele ta dalwa e li omunhu a wanenena * , nokwa fya ponhele yetu .
Osho oshe shi ningifa tashi shiiva opo tu kale tu na ekwatafano naKalunga nosho yo eteelelo loku ka mona omwenyo waalushe .
Omolwashike Jesus a li e na okufya opo tu dule okukulilwa moulunde ?
Mbela Kalunga Omunaenghono adishe ka li ta dulu okulongifa onghedi imwe ihe fi ekuliloyambo laJesus , opo a yandje omwenyo waalushe koludalo laAdam ?
Ngeno Kalunga okwa taulukile omhango oyo , ovanhu otashi dulika ngeno va kale va limbililwa kutya nomoinima imwe pamwe osho ha ningi .
Pashihopaenenwa , otashi dulika ve lipule kutya , ota ka tokola ngoo pauyuki kutya oolyelye vomoludalo laAdam va wana oku ka mona omwenyo waalushe ?
Mbela ngeno ovanhu otava ka kala ngoo ve na elineekelo kutya ota ka wanifa po omaudaneko aye ?
Ndele molwaashi Kalunga omuyuki , otu na elineekelo kutya ashishe osho ta longo oshi li mondjila .
Kalunga okwe tu yeululila omhito yoku ka kala nomwenyo waalushe mOparadisa kombada yedu , e shi ninga okupitila mekuliloyambo laJesus .
Jesus okwa popya muJohannes 3 : 16 a ti : “ Osheshi osho Kalunga a kala e hole ounyuni , Oye a yandja Omona waye Ewifa , opo keshe ou te mu itavele a ha kane , ndelenee a kale e nomwenyo waalushe . ”
Efyo laJesus ola ulika kutya Kalunga omuyuki noku hole ovanhu nohole inene .
Omolwashike Jesus a li e na okuhepekwa nokufya efyo liyahameka ngaashi sha popiwa mOmavangeli ?
Mokulididimikila omayeleko nokukanyatela oudiinini , Jesus okwa nyaneka pomutenya oipupulu yOndiaboli eshi ya ti kutya ovanhu itava dulu okukala ovadiinini kuKalunga ngeenge ve li moudjuu .
