Ndele Jesus oo a li a wanenena ngaashi Adam , okwa kala omudiinini nonande okwa li ta hepekwa .
( 1 Ovakorinto 15 : 45 ) Kungaho okwa ulika kutya Adam ngeno okwa dulikile kuKalunga ngeno naye okwa pondola .
Jesus okwe tu tulila po oshihopaenenwa eshi e lididimikila omashongo .
( 1 Petrus 2 : 21 ) Molwaashi Jesus okwa kala ha dulika , Kalunga okwe mu pa ondjabi yoku kala nomwenyo waalushe meulu .
Jesus okwa popya kutya oshike tu na okuninga eshi a ti : “ Nomwenyo waalushe owo tuu ou , vo ve ku shiive , Oove auke Kalunga kashili , naau we mu tuma , Jesus Kristus . ” — Johannes 17 : 3 .
Ovanyanyangidi voshifo eshi otave ku ladipike u lihonge kombinga yaJehova Kalunga kashili nosho yo Omona waye , Jesus Kristus .
